;TYPE:Custom
M862.3 P "MK3S" ; printer model check
M862.1 P0.4 ; nozzle diameter check
M115 U3.14.1 ; tell printer latest fw version
G90 ; use absolute coordinates
M83 ; extruder relative mode
M104 S240 ; set extruder temp
M140 S90 ; set bed temp
M190 S90 ; wait for bed temp
M109 S240 ; wait for extruder temp
G28 W ; home all without mesh bed level
G80 X107.219 Y85.5176 W35.5628 H38.9681 ; mesh bed levelling

G1 Z0.2 F720
G1 Y-3 F1000 ; go outside print area
G92 E0
G1 X60 E9 F1000 ; intro line
G1 X100 E12.5 F1000 ; intro line

G92 E0
M221 S95

