M907 E430 ; set extruder motor current
G21 ; set units to millimeters
G90 ; use absolute coordinates
M83 ; use relative distances for extrusion

M900 K0.08 ; Filament gcode LA 1.5
M900 K45 ; Filament gcode LA 1.0




